Syntax:-

selector{
    property:value;
    property:value;
    property:value;
}

selctor--- is an identity to pick an element in html
    simple
        element, id(#), class(.)
    combinator
        descandant( ), chid(>), adjucent sibiling(+), general sibling(~)
    pseudo class
        :link, :visited, :hover, :active
    pseudo element
        ::firest-line, ::last-line, ::first-letter
    attribute selctor


color